      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Daniel Homan</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:197px;\"><a href=\"http://personal.denison.edu/~homand/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1/1e/DanHoman.jpg\" width=\"195\" height=\"293\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:DanHoman.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Danien Homan <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Daniel C. Homan</b>,<br />\nan American <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astrophysics\">astrophysicist</a> and associate professor at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denison_University\">Denison University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Granville,_Ohio\">Granville, Ohio</a>. \nHe received his Ph.D. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physics\">physics</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brandeis_University\">Brandeis University</a> in 1999. As avocational computer chess programmer Daniel Homan is author of the experimental <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/EXchess\" title=\"EXchess\">EXchess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#1997_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1997 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2000_..._2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2010_..._2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.brandeis.edu/departments/physics/people/faculty/wardle.html\">John F.C. Wardle</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>Detection and Measurement of Parsec-Scale Circular Polarization in Four AGN</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0007396\">arXiv:astro-ph/0007396</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> et al. (<b>2000</b>). <i>Parsec-Scale Blazar Monitoring: Proper Motions</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0009301\">arXiv:astro-ph/0009301</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.brandeis.edu/departments/physics/people/faculty/wardle.html\">John F.C. Wardle</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>The Nature of Jets: Evidence from Circular Polarization Observations</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0011515\">arXiv:astro-ph/0011515</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> et al. (<b>2002</b>).  <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/338701\">Parsec-Scale Blazar Monitoring: Flux and Polarization Variability</a></i>.<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Astrophysical_Journal\">The Astrophysical Journal</a>, Vol. 568</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Physical Properties of Jets in AGN</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1110.4852\">arXiv:1110.4852</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Inverse Depolarization: A Potential Probe of Internal Faraday Rotation and Helical Magnetic Fields in Extragalactic Radio Jets</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1202.1650\">arXiv:1202.1650</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel C. Homan</a> et al. (<b>2014</b>).  <i>MOJAVE XII: Acceleration and Collimation of Blazar Jets on Parsec Scales</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1410.8502\">arXiv:1410.8502</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1997_...\">1997 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 1997 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/d_EPBy6QcwI/b8c6piRlRlUJ\">Evolutionary Evaluation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, September 09, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=10471\">Hash collisions (was Re: Let's analyze move 36)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 1997&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#Collisions\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Collisions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=13011\">First win against a crafty clone</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 16, 1997</li></ul>\n<p><b>1998</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=13993\">Extensions?!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 13, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=14685\">Artificial Intelligence</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 126, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=16136\">Opponent specific learning...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 26, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">Learning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=16657\">New version of EXchess released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 08, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=20074\">Re: Programmer vs Program strength</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 05, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=21700\">Stupidity, Programming, and Me&#160;;)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=24669\">Small number statistics and small differences</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Match_Statistics\" title=\"Match Statistics\">Match Statistics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=24978\">Re: Waltzing Matilda (was: statistics, 10 events tell us what&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 17, 1998</li></ul>\n<p><b>1999</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=42909\">A Null Move Enhancement?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=43378\">Re: Review of ALEXS by Larry Kaufman</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Alexs\" title=\"Alexs\">Alexs</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=51608\">mtdf</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 13, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=60557\">Move Make/Unmake Questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 15, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Copy-Make\" title=\"Copy-Make\">Copy-Make</a>, <a href=\"/Unmake_Move\" title=\"Unmake Move\">Unmake Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=65039\">ETC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 17, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Enhanced_Transposition_Cutoff\" title=\"Enhanced Transposition Cutoff\">Enhanced Transposition Cutoff</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=68825\">Move Ordering at the Root</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=75430\">Releasing the Source Code?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 1999 </li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_..._2\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=117970\">Pseudo-code for TD learning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 06, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Temporal_Difference_Learning\" title=\"Temporal Difference Learning\">Temporal Difference Learning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=139716\">New version of EXchess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=483082\">New Version of EXchess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Januaray 29, 2006</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_..._2\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Homan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43513\">A search enhancement?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 30, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning#MoveCountBasedPruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Move Count Based Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44749\">Move ordering idea (old and new?)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 09, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Countermove_Heuristic\" title=\"Countermove Heuristic\">Countermove Heuristic</a>, <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46858\">Lazy SMP, part 2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel Homan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48536\">Lazy SMP and Work Sharing</a> by  <a class=\"mw-selflink self